<subSubSection pageId="1" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1638,1957]" pageId="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,1788,1813]" pageId="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This species can be distinguish from the other Neotropical taxa of its subgenus by the coloration of the legs, especially evident on the yellow of the metatibia grading to dark brown proximally in 
<taxonomicName box="[1217,1319,1824,1848]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Habronyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavus">
<emphasis box="[1217,1319,1824,1848]" italics="true" pageId="1">H. flavus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, while the metatibia is blackish grading to dark brown proximally in 
<taxonomicName box="[803,921,1861,1884]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Habronyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ariasae">
<emphasis box="[803,921,1861,1884]" italics="true" pageId="1">H. ariasae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and is entirely black in 
<taxonomicName box="[1190,1332,1861,1884]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Habronyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carmonai">
<emphasis box="[1190,1332,1861,1884]" italics="true" pageId="1">H. carmonai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="3" pageId="1" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1638,1957]" pageId="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1896,1921]" pageId="1">Description.</emphasis>
Female: Fore wing length 
<quantity box="[653,736,1896,1920]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="1" unit="mm" value="14.0">14 mm</quantity>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[800,908,1897,1921]" pageId="1">paratypes</typeStatus>
are slightly smaller, with fore wing lengths of 
<quantity box="[151,275,1933,1957]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.04" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="0.78" pageId="1" unit="mm" value="10.4" valueMax="13.0" valueMin="7.8">7.8–13mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1930,1983]" pageId="2">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,421,1930,1952]" pageId="2">
<collectionCode box="[151,234,1930,1952]" pageId="2">PLATE</collectionCode>
<number box="[239,251,1930,1952]" pageId="2" value="1.0">1</number>
FIGURES 
<number box="[376,415,1930,1952]" pageId="2" value="2.0" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="1.0">1–3</number>
.
</emphasis>
Details of 
<taxonomicName authority="Alvarado" authorityName="Alvarado" box="[531,966,1930,1952]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Habronyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavus" status="new species" subGenus="Camposcopus">
